data.description: STUNNING custom built home featuring a bright, open floor plan design that brings breath-taking golf course and lake views into your home. This estate leaves nothing to be desired with its high-end hardwood floors, lovely old world architecture, amazing master suite with an extremely spacious walk-in closet, his & hers vanities, custom cabinets, tall ceilings, 8ft doors, plantation shutters, tankless hot water heater, gas fireplace and an irrigation system that runs off well water, just to name a few! Not to mention, yard maintenance is included in your HOA fees!! The home also offers an exquisite outdoor living area that is the perfect spot to watch the sunset over the 17th hole of Craft Farms Arnold Palmer designed golf course. MUST SEE!!
